snippet.textDisplay:
Quick tutorial! 🤗

Nationality: the country (-ies) you have citizenship from

Race: what you look like (for the most part)

Ethnicity : tracing your DNA to where your ancestors were from

Religion : the belief system you follow.

Eg:
I am a BLACK (race) IGBO (ethnicity) NIGERIAN (nationality) CHRISTIAN (religion).
Someone could be a: WHITE (race) SWEDISH (ethnicity) AMERICAN (nationality) ATHEIST (religion)
